  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Claymore Clan, Level 12+<br />Your drive to protect and survive allows you to outperform lesser warriors. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You gain the <em><strong>Decisive Parry</strong></em> jutsu and if you had it already you instead gain another Claymore Hijutsu of your choice. The casting time of Decisive Parry becomes \"1 Reaction, when you or a creature you can see within range of your movement speed would be hit by an attack.\" You become the target of this attack as long as you move within 5 feet of the creature who was originally targeted.</li><li>Creatures of your choice within 5 feet of you other than you, are counted as being in half cover.</li><li>Once per rest when you become bloodied you may immediately cast <em><strong>Warrior's Resolve</strong></em> at no action cost.</li></ul>",
